fkk.ac.th is the official website of Fakkwan Wittayakom School, a Thai secondary school located in Phayao Province, Thailand. The school operates under the Office of the Basic Education Commission and provides general secondary education across subjects including science, mathematics, languages, and vocational training.

The website serves as a central hub for educational activities, administrative announcements, student affairs, teaching staff information, and public school events. It also publishes achievements, school news, academic calendars, and supports digital documentation and e-office systems for internal use.

Teligent Telecom AB – Teligent Telecom is a Swedish telecommunications technology company founded in 1990 and headquartered in Danderyd, Stockholm. Teligent specializes in developing advanced service platforms and solutions for telecom operators, including messaging systems, Voice over IP (VoIP), mass calling, and service delivery platforms (SDP). The company is known for its scalable and flexible architecture, such as the P90/E platform, which enables operators to rapidly deploy and manage telecom services. Teligent provides its solutions to a global client base, supporting both traditional and next-generation network environments.
